page_content: The page is about the Kantonsarztamt (KAA), a reference center for public health in the Canton of Fribourg.
The page discusses "Heilmittel," covering areas such as pharmaceuticals, blood products, and medical devices.
The page is about "Supply Chain Tools," an interactive collection of tools for sustainable supply chain management, including software solutions.
The page provides information about Gabriel Kolly, a member of the Grosser Rat des Kantons Freiburg, including his roles, mandates, and activities.
The page provides information on courses for "Gehörbildung und Musiklehre," focusing on music theory and ear training.
The page serves as a guide for using DSK2, a software for managing technical documents related to land mutations and other geomatics tasks.
The page is a guide on how to use the "Aktensuche" (File Search) feature in the DSK2 software for geomatics and land management tasks.
